hob ikh genumen a goy, ibergeforn di Vaysl,

00:21:18.073 --> 00:21:19.159
un kh'hob dort,

00:21:19.159 --> 00:21:24.950
dort hot men mir gezogt, m'hot gezen, ober vu zi iz veys men nisht. nakher ⟨iz zi⟩ gekumen vayter, zogt zi ⟨dos, UNK⟩

00:21:24.950 --> 00:21:26.033
⟨zol arumg⟩⟨UNK⟩.

00:21:26.055 --> 00:21:29.958
alzo, bin ikh aleynt vayter geforn. s'iz shoyn geven mentshn, zenen, zenen,

00:21:29.958 --> 00:21:33.216
zenen gekumen fun, fun der milkhome, ⟨z-⟩ ot azoy, kh'veys dokh,

00:21:33.216 --> 00:21:34.925
zenen alts ⟨aru-⟩ gelofn.

00:21:35.134 --> 00:21:37.870
hot men gezogt mir az

00:21:37.870 --> 00:21:39.678
zi iz in Volomin.

00:21:39.678 --> 00:21:42.218
a, a betlerin hot ir gehat,

00:21:42.218 --> 00:21:45.523
zi iz fun Volomin, un zi heyst azoy un azoy.

00:21:45.833 --> 00:21:50.020
alzo, zi hot mikh gematert. ikh bin geforn vayter.

00:21:50.270 --> 00:21:54.545
UNK ⟨gekhap- iz, iz ge-⟩ nisht geven keyn, keyn, keyn TRAINS nokh

00:21:54.545 --> 00:21:56.846
mit mentshn, nor militer.

00:21:56.903 --> 00:22:00.221
hob ikh zikh oyfgekhapt oyf a TRAIN vos er geyt in yenem UNK

00:22:01.273 --> 00:22:04.389
keyn, keyn Volo- Volomin hot ⟨zi⟩ geheysn, di shtot.

00:22:04.817 --> 00:22:09.907
alzo, ikh kum on mit der ban keyn Volomin. di f- di ban shteyt zikh nisht; fort mit zelner, fort avek keyn Moskve.

00:22:09.913 --> 00:22:11.410
alzo, vos tu ikh do?

00:22:11.410 --> 00:22:15.450
un s'iz geven aza barg zamd UNK a tants arop. kh'hob gekont geharget vern.

00:22:15.938 --> 00:22:18.379
⟨un fun⟩ dort, ikh hob gemuzt geyn in shtot arayn.

00:22:18.385 --> 00:22:21.270
ikh bin gekumen in shtot arayn, shoyn geven far nakht.

00:22:21.793 --> 00:22:25.089
alzo, kh'hob ibergenekhtikt... s'iz shoyn geven a por yidn...

00:22:25.089 --> 00:22:29.043
alzo, kh'hob ibergenekhtikt, un ikh hob ge- nokhgefregt zikh UNK s'iz do a komitet.

00:22:29.151 --> 00:22:31.339
bin ikh gegangen in komitet: me ken di goye.

00:22:31.648 --> 00:22:35.720
ken. hot mikh a BOY avekgefirt tsu di goye. ikh kum arayn dort tsu di goye.

00:22:35.720 --> 00:22:38.510
zogt zi, "yo. ikh ⟨vel⟩ dir gebn an adres vu zi iz."

00:22:38.702 --> 00:22:41.255
 ⟨iz, IMAGINE,⟩ zi iz geven fun mir

00:22:41.255 --> 00:22:42.628
tsen kilometer!

00:22:43.073 --> 00:22:44.889
zogt zi, "for do

00:22:45.891 --> 00:22:48.956
k- keyn Brudne, keyn Brudne; dort iz zi do."

00:22:49.131 --> 00:22:52.432
alzo, ikh bin gekumen tsu forn fun, fun dos.

00:22:52.523 --> 00:22:58.561
kh'hob ⟨n-⟩ kh'hob gemuzt zayn in Varshe, hob ikh gefirt z⟨a⟩⟨UNK⟩. ikh hob n- kh'hob nokh gehat a sod oykh dernokh dem, a, mit frukht, mit,

00:22:58.561 --> 00:23:00.611
mit mayns a kuzin, mit tsvey goyim...

00:23:00.611 --> 00:23:02.239
dos loynt zikh nisht tsu fartseyln...

00:23:02.239 --> 00:23:03.350
nor vos den?

00:23:03.475 --> 00:23:11.096
