00:23:11.203 --> 00:23:13.306
alzo, ⟨zi iz geven,⟩ zi hot ir gebrengt!

00:23:14.427 --> 00:23:18.724
zi iz geven bar a bo- bar a, bar a betlerin vos zi betlt.

00:23:19.101 --> 00:23:25.063
zi iz geven azoy bakrokhn mit dos, yents. m'hot ir arayngezetst bald in a, dos, un opgevashn, dos, yents.

00:23:25.063 --> 00:23:28.007
m'iz gegangen bald tsu a dokter. zogt er, me muz ⟨ir⟩ avekshikn...

00:23:28.007 --> 00:23:29.399
s'iz shoyn geven aza,

00:23:29.399 --> 00:23:31.582
far di kinder, aza pansyonatn,

00:23:32.128 --> 00:23:33.776
keyn, dos,

00:23:33.850 --> 00:23:37.658
nokh Varshe... bald, vi azoy hey-... Otvotsk! OTWOCK.

00:23:37.883 --> 00:23:40.189
far tuberkuloz iz dort gevezn.

00:23:40.549 --> 00:23:45.090
alzo, dort hot men ir avekgefirt, un dort iz zi geven

00:23:45.325 --> 00:23:47.988
dray, fir monat, un zi iz gekumen tsu zikh,

00:23:47.988 --> 00:23:49.456
un zi iz gekumen aheym.

00:23:49.456 --> 00:23:50.679
⟨zi iz geven mit⟩ UNK

00:23:50.679 --> 00:23:52.710
⟨zi iz geven⟩ azoy lang bizkl vanet...

00:23:53.104 --> 00:23:56.540
di, di, di, di, di muter hot gehat

00:23:57.340 --> 00:23:59.882
a shvester UNK in Amerike.

00:23:59.972 --> 00:24:03.386
vi azoy zi hot geheysn veys men nisht, hot mayn froy geshribn

00:24:03.386 --> 00:24:04.742
tsu ire shvesters

00:24:05.220 --> 00:24:08.111
a briv keyn Amerike,

00:24:08.111 --> 00:24:10.710
in Amerike zoln zey shteln in PAPER

00:24:10.710 --> 00:24:14.445
az mir zukhn. s'iz gekumen, dos. un zey hobn zi dernokh dem aribergenumen.

00:24:14.721 --> 00:24:17.941
un ikh vil visn vegn aykh yetst in di tsayt.

00:24:17.941 --> 00:24:23.254
vos i- vi lang hot ir gelebt dort, un, un fun van- vi zaynt ir avekgeforn?

00:24:18.030 --> 00:24:18.830
yo.

00:24:22.737 --> 00:24:26.614
nakher, nakher iz gekumen a, a,

00:24:26.614 --> 00:24:30.622
vos er iz geven a POLICEMAN in der geto oykhet, nor er hot zikh nisht geshtelt tsu di dos,

00:24:30.622 --> 00:24:32.180
UNK er iz antlofn.

00:24:32.811 --> 00:24:34.965
di vayb mit di kinder UNK tsugenumen.

00:24:35.072 --> 00:24:39.082
un er, er iz geven a groyser kombinator, aza kluger man.

00:24:39.190 --> 00:24:42.272
er lebt shoyn nisht oykhet. er iz geven y- a sakh yinger fun mir.

00:24:43.257 --> 00:24:48.097
un er zogt, "in Vrotslav"... er hot zikh gemakht, er iz geven a komunist, ⟨a do-⟩ papirn gehat...

00:24:48.097 --> 00:24:49.775
"in Vrotslav," zogt er,

00:24:49.775 --> 00:24:50.962
"hob ikh dort

00:24:51.019 --> 00:24:53.066
genumen a bekeray,

00:24:53.066 --> 00:24:55.350
a mekhanishe bekeray,"

00:24:55.350 --> 00:24:56.446
zogt er,

00:24:57.212 --> 00:25:00.668
velekhes, az er hot gevizn, ⟨er iz⟩ a komunist, hot er ⟨nes⟩ gekrign.

00:25:00.668 --> 00:25:02.904
di doytshn hobn dokh aroysgeyogt dort.

00:25:02.904 --> 00:25:07.800
alzo, zogt er, "du bist dokh a beker," ⟨un shoyn⟩. zogt er,

00:25:07.800 --> 00:25:10.160
"kum tsu forn, ⟨vel⟩'mir zayn shutfim."

00:25:10.160 --> 00:25:13.288
alzo, kh'bin gekumen tsu ⟨b- forn, forn⟩ dort ahin,

00:25:13.632 --> 00:25:15.550
