00:25:13.733 --> 00:25:14.739
⟨u⟩n...

00:25:15.268 --> 00:25:17.590
nisht meyn vi a, vi a, a yor.

00:25:17.597 --> 00:25:18.840
un dernokh dem?

00:25:18.120 --> 00:25:20.763
⟨kh'hob genumen,⟩ m'hot ongehoybn tsu hargenen, zey hargenen yidn.

00:25:20.770 --> 00:25:25.205
kh'hob dort gehat a, UNK aza ⟨porets⟩, a mekhanishe bekeray,

00:25:25.205 --> 00:25:26.209
un m'hot gehat

00:25:26.209 --> 00:25:28.039
eyn froy vos zi hot tsugenumen

00:25:28.039 --> 00:25:30.483
