azoyne gefangene vos zey hobn ger⟨UNK⟩ gereynikt di, di, di, di BRICKS

00:25:42.623 --> 00:25:45.570
fun di, fun di bombes vos... yo.

00:25:45.570 --> 00:25:47.058
