00:25:47.058 --> 00:25:48.265
a kapitan

00:25:48.265 --> 00:25:52.020
a man in England, ⟨hot zi⟩. UNK

00:25:52.020 --> 00:25:53.386
zi hot gekrign,

00:25:53.386 --> 00:25:55.402
a zlot hot zi gekrign

00:25:55.402 --> 00:25:56.811
fun yeder broyt,

00:25:56.811 --> 00:25:58.462
